===message:Although I agree with you that the national banking system was necessary, I also feel that ending slavey was the important aspect of the war.  Slavery was the moral and political foundation of southern society.  Ending slavery was a direct attack on the Confederate Constitution.  Also, how ironic that the fall of Atlanta and the Sherman's March through Georgia greatly contributed to the fall of southern society.
